<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lv">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=794, height=1123, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Rēķins {{ invoice_number }}</title>
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-ext-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-ext-500-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-500-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-ext-600-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-600-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Inter';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/inter-latin-ext-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Inter';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/inter-latin-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }

        @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        /* Page shell: A4 in mm. (595×842px is only ~157×223mm at CSS 96dpi — not full A4.) */
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm;
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
        }

        .page {
            position: relative;
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm;
            background: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
        }

        /* ~33px @ 96dpi — как в исходном Figma; ближе к эталону A4 по полям */
        .page-box {
            position: absolute;
            left: 8.73mm;
            top: 8.73mm;
            right: 8.73mm;
            bottom: 8.73mm;
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .header-region {
            flex: 0 0 auto;
        }

        .header-region .page-rail-530 {
            zoom: 1.12;
        }

        .body-region {
            flex: 1 1 0;
            min-height: 0;
            margin-top: 57px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-region {
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .footer-region .page-rail-530 {
            zoom: 1.12;
        }

        /* Rail шире эталонной колонки 500px после zoom */
        .page-rail-530 {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* --- Header --- */
        .invoice-header {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .invoice-header-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .invoice-header-left {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: flex-start;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            width: 288.53px;
            max-width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            gap: 18px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .invoice-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18.2439px;
            line-height: 22px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .invoice-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 28px;
            min-width: 0;
            flex: 1 1 auto;
        }

        .invoice-meta-block {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .invoice-meta-label {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 7px;
            line-height: 9px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .invoice-meta-value {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            margin-top: 2px;
            padding: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .invoice-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .invoice-brand img {
            display: block;
            width: 112.32px;
            height: 15.97px;
            object-fit: contain;
            object-position: right center;
        }

        .invoice-header-divider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border-radius: 3.42073px;
            border: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* --- Main --- */
        .invoice-main {
            width: 500px;
            max-width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 46px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            zoom: 1.22;
        }

        /* --- Party --- */
        .party-section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 240px 240px;
            column-gap: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .party-column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 9px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .party-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .party-divider {
            height: 0.47px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border-radius: 3.42073px;
            border: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .party-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 11.33px;
        }

        .field-stack {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2.28px;
        }

        .field-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 25.09px;
        }

        .field-row .field-stack {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .field-label {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 7px;
            line-height: 9px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .field-value {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        /* --- Route + service --- */
        .route-service-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 46px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .route-map-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 240px 240px;
            column-gap: 20px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .route-column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .route-title-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .icon-bubble {
            width: 23.84px;
            height: 23.84px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #D7FF01;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            padding: 4.77px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .icon-bubble img {
            width: 13.11px;
            height: 13.11px;
            display: block;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .icon-bubble--service {
            width: 22.56px;
            height: 22.56px;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .icon-bubble--service img {
            width: 11.28px;
            height: 11.28px;
        }

        .icon-bubble--pay {
            width: 22.8px;
            height: 22.8px;
            padding: 4.56px;
        }

        .icon-bubble--pay img {
            width: 9px;
            height: 9px;
        }

        .route-title-text,
        .service-title-text,
        .payment-title-text {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .route-divider,
        .service-divider,
        .payment-divider {
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .route-stops-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 19px 1fr;
            column-gap: 9.12px;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .route-marker-column {
            position: relative;
            width: 19px;
            min-height: 56px;
        }

        .route-marker-column::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 8.5px;
            top: 9.12px;
            bottom: 9.12px;
            width: 1.14px;
            background: #000;
            border-radius: 3.42073px;
        }

        .route-marker-top,
        .route-marker-bottom {
            width: 9.12px;
            height: 9.12px;
            border: 1.14024px solid #000;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fff;
            position: absolute;
            left: 4px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .route-marker-top { top: 0; }
        .route-marker-bottom { bottom: 0; }

        .route-text-side {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .route-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2.28px;
        }

        .route-small-label {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 6.84145px;
            line-height: 8px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .route-value {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9.12193px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .route-inner-divider {
            margin: 8px 0 8px 28.506px;
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .map-column {
            width: 240px;
        }

        .map-preview {
            width: 240px;
            height: 118px;
            border-radius: 7.98169px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: block;
            position: relative;
            background: #e8e8e8;
        }

        .map-box-inner {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        .map-box-inner .map-tile-img {
            position: absolute;
            display: block;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
        }

        .map-box-inner img.map-fill {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center;
            display: block;
        }

        .map-pin-img {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 2;
            pointer-events: none;
            display: block;
            width: 13px;
            height: auto;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        /* --- Service --- */
        .service-block {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 9px;
        }

        .service-header-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .service-title-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4.56px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .service-date {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            text-align: right;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            max-width: 55%;
        }

        .service-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 53px 53px 61px 53px 53px 58px;
            column-gap: 28px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .service-cell {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2.28px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .service-cell:last-child {
            align-items: flex-end;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .service-label {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 6.84145px;
            line-height: 8px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            white-space: normal;
        }

        .service-value {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9.12193px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .service-cell:last-child .service-value {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* --- Payment --- */
        .payment-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .payment-head {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 9px;
        }

        .payment-title-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4.56px;
        }

        .payment-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 9px;
        }

        .payment-info-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 59px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .payment-info-col {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2.28px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .payment-legal {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 7px;
            line-height: 9px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            max-width: 213px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .payment-legal p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .payment-legal p + p {
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* --- Footer --- */
        .invoice-footer {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            padding-top: 16px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .invoice-footer-divider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border-radius: 3.42073px;
            border: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .invoice-footer-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 9.44px;
        }

        .invoice-footer-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .invoice-footer-left img {
            height: 10px;
            width: auto;
            display: block;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .invoice-footer-right {
            max-width: 310.15px;
            text-align: right;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .footer-small {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 6px;
            line-height: 7px;
            color: #22201F;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
    <div class="page-box">
        <div class="header-region">
            <div class="page-rail-530">
                <header class="invoice-header">
                    <div class="invoice-header-row">
                        <div class="invoice-header-left">
                            <h1 class="invoice-title">Rēķins</h1>
                            <div class="invoice-meta">
                                <div class="invoice-meta-block">
                                    <div class="invoice-meta-label">Rēķina Nr / Pasūtījuma Nr</div>
                                    <div class="invoice-meta-value">{{ invoice_number }}</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="invoice-meta-block">
                                    <div class="invoice-meta-label">Rēķina datums:</div>
                                    <div class="invoice-meta-value">{{ issue_date }}</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="invoice-brand">
                            <img src="invoice-assets/group-1122.svg" width="112" height="16" alt="hevvi">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="invoice-header-divider" />
                </header>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="body-region">
        <main class="invoice-main">
            <section class="party-section">
                <div class="party-column">
                    <div class="party-title">Pakalpojuma sniedzējs</div>
                    <hr class="party-divider" />
                    <div class="party-content">
                        <div class="field-stack">
                            <div class="field-label">Pārdevējs (Pakalpojuma sniedzējs):</div>
                            <div class="field-value">{{ seller_name }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field-row">
                            <div class="field-stack">
                                <div class="field-label">Reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="field-value">{{ seller_reg }}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field-stack">
                                <div class="field-label">PVN reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="field-value">{{ seller_vat }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field-stack">
                            <div class="field-label">Juridiskā adrese:</div>
                            <div class="field-value">{{ seller_line1 }}</div>
                            {% if seller_line2 %}<div class="field-value" style="margin-top: 4px;">{{ seller_line2 }}</div>{% endif %}
                        </div>
                        <div class="field-row">
                            <div class="field-stack">
                                <div class="field-label">E-pasts:</div>
                                <div class="field-value">{{ seller_email }}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field-stack">
                                <div class="field-label">Tālrunis:</div>
                                <div class="field-value">{{ seller_phone }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="party-column">
                    <div class="party-title">Pakalpojumu saņēmējs</div>
                    <hr class="party-divider" />
                    <div class="party-content">
                        <div class="field-stack">
                            <div class="field-label">Pircējs (Klients):</div>
                            <div class="field-value">{{ buyer_company }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field-row">
                            <div class="field-stack">
                                <div class="field-label">Reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="field-value">{{ buyer_reg }}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field-stack">
                                <div class="field-label">PVN reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="field-value">{{ buyer_vat }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field-stack">
                            <div class="field-label">Adrese:</div>
                            {% for line in buyer_address_lines %}
                                <div class="field-value"{% if not loop.first %} style="margin-top: 4px;"{% endif %}>{{ line }}</div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="route-service-section">
                <div class="route-map-row">
                    <div class="route-column">
                        <div class="route-title-row">
                            <span class="icon-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><img src="invoice-assets/fi-446075.svg" alt=""></span>
                            <span class="route-title-text">Maršruts</span>
                        </div>
                        <hr class="route-divider" />
                        <div class="route-stops-layout">
                            <div class="route-marker-column">
                                <span class="route-marker-top" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="route-marker-bottom" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="route-text-side">
                                <div class="route-text">
                                    <div class="route-small-label">Pickup</div>
                                    <div class="route-value">{{ pickup }}</div>
                                </div>
                                <hr class="route-inner-divider" />
                                <div class="route-text">
                                    <div class="route-small-label">Delivery</div>
                                    <div class="route-value">{{ delivery }}</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr class="route-divider" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="map-column">
                        <div class="map-preview">
                            <div class="map-box-inner">
                                {% if map_show_pins and map_inner_w and map_inner_h and map_img_w %}
                                    <img class="map-tile-img" src="{{ map_data_uri|raw }}" alt=""
                                         style="left: {{ map_img_left }}px; top: {{ map_img_top }}px; width: {{ map_img_w }}px; height: {{ map_img_h }}px;">
                                {% else %}
                                    <img class="map-fill" src="{{ map_data_uri|raw }}" alt="">
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if map_show_pins and map_inner_w and map_inner_h %}
                                    <img class="map-pin-img" src="invoice-assets/map-pin-pickup.svg" width="13" height="15" alt=""
                                         style="left: {{ map_pickup_left }}px; top: {{ map_pickup_top }}px;">
                                    <img class="map-pin-img" src="invoice-assets/map-pin-drop.svg" width="13" height="15" alt=""
                                         style="left: {{ map_drop_left }}px; top: {{ map_drop_top }}px;">
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-block">
                    <div class="service-header-row">
                        <div class="service-title-row">
                            <span class="icon-bubble icon-bubble--service" aria-hidden="true"><img src="invoice-assets/delivered-1.svg" alt=""></span>
                            <span class="service-title-text">Pakalpojums</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-date">Pakalpojuma sniegšanas datums: {{ service_date }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="service-divider" />
                    <div class="service-grid">
                        <div class="service-cell">
                            <div class="service-label">Kravas piegādes maksa</div>
                            <div class="service-value">{{ amount_freight }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-cell">
                            <div class="service-label">Cena bez PVN</div>
                            <div class="service-value">{{ amount_cena_bez_pvn }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-cell">
                            <div class="service-label">{{ commission_label }}</div>
                            <div class="service-value">{{ amount_commission }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-cell">
                            <div class="service-label">Starpsumma (bez PVN)</div>
                            <div class="service-value">{{ amount_subtotal }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-cell">
                            <div class="service-label">{{ vat_label }}</div>
                            <div class="service-value">{{ amount_vat }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-cell">
                            <div class="service-label">KOPĀ APMAKSAI (ar PVN)</div>
                            <div class="service-value">{{ amount_gross }}</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="payment-section">
                <div class="payment-head">
                    <div class="payment-title-row">
                        <span class="icon-bubble icon-bubble--pay" aria-hidden="true"><img src="invoice-assets/fi-157977.svg" alt=""></span>
                        <span class="payment-title-text">Maksājuma informācija</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="payment-divider" />
                </div>
                <div class="payment-content">
                    <div class="payment-info-row">
                        <div class="payment-info-col">
                            <div class="field-label">Maksājuma veids:</div>
                            <div class="field-value">{{ payment_method }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="payment-info-col">
                            <div class="field-label">Maksājuma statuss:</div>
                            <div class="field-value">{{ payment_status }}</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="payment-legal">
                        <p>Rēķins sagatavots elektroniski un ir derīgs bez paraksta</p>
                        <p>PVN piemērots saskaņā ar Pievienotās vērtības nodokļa likumu</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-region">
            <div class="page-rail-530">
                <footer class="invoice-footer">
                    <hr class="invoice-footer-divider" />
                    <div class="invoice-footer-row">
                        <div class="invoice-footer-left">
                            <img src="invoice-assets/group-1123.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
                            <span class="footer-small">Pakalpojums sniegts caur Hevvi digitālo platformu</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="invoice-footer-right">
                            <span class="footer-small">Hevvi App nodrošina digitālu platformu transporta pakalpojumu organizēšanai. Komisijas maksa tiek ieturēta par platformas izmantošanu un administrēšanu.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </footer>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
